TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT dbo.dim_product.product_key as product_key, dbo.dim_product.product_name as product_name, dbo.dim_product.Product_description as Product_description, dbo.dim_product.product_subcategory as product_subcategory, dbo.dim_product.product_category as product_category, dbo.dim_product.color as color, dbo.dim_product.model_name as model_name, dbo.dim_product.reorder_point as reorder_point, dbo.dim_product.standard_cost as standard_cost, dbo.dim_product.source_system_code as source_system_code, dbo.dim_product.start_date as start_date, dbo.dim_product.end_date as end_date, dbo.dim_product.is_current as is_current, dbo.dim_product.product_id as product_id FROM dbo.dim_product WHERE end_date IS NULL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( ( MD5( ProductID || O_Product_Name || O_Product_decribtion || O_Product_subcategory || O_Product_Category || O_Color || O_Model_name || ReorderPoint || StandardCost || O_Source_System || ModifiedDate ) != MD5( LKB_product_id || LKB_product_name || LKB_Product_description || LKB_Product_subcategory || LKB_product_category || LKB_color || LKB_model_name || LKB_reorder_point || LKB_standard_cost || LKB_source_system_code || LKB_start_date ) ), 1, 0 )
